sequenceDiagram
    autonumber

    participant Browser as Browser / Client
    participant KAP as kube-auth-proxy<br/>4180/TCP HTTP
    participant OIDC as OIDC Provider<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    participant OSAuth as OpenShift OAuth<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    participant Upstream as Upstream App
    participant Redis as Redis (optional)<br/>6379/TCP
    participant Envoy as Envoy (ext_authz)

    rect rgb(232, 244, 253)
        Note over Browser,Upstream: Flow 1: OIDC Authentication
        Browser->>KAP: GET /oauth2/start<br/>No auth
        KAP->>KAP: Generate CSRF cookie + PKCE verifier
        KAP->>Browser: 302 Redirect to OIDC /authorize<br/>Set-Cookie: _oauth2_proxy_csrf
        Browser->>OIDC: GET /authorize?client_id=...&code_challenge=...<br/>User logs in
        OIDC->>Browser: 302 Redirect to /oauth2/callback<br/>?code=AUTH_CODE&state=STATE
        Browser->>KAP: GET /oauth2/callback?code=AUTH_CODE<br/>Cookie: _oauth2_proxy_csrf
        KAP->>KAP: Validate CSRF + state
        KAP->>OIDC: POST /token<br/>Auth: Client ID/Secret + auth code + PKCE verifier
        OIDC-->>KAP: Access Token + ID Token + Refresh Token
        KAP->>KAP: Verify ID Token (JWKS)
        KAP->>Redis: Store session (if Redis configured)
        KAP->>Browser: 302 Redirect to original URL<br/>Set-Cookie: _oauth2_proxy (session)
    end

    rect rgb(213, 232, 212)
        Note over Browser,Upstream: Flow 2: Authenticated Upstream Request
        Browser->>KAP: GET /app/resource<br/>Cookie: _oauth2_proxy
        KAP->>KAP: Load + validate session
        opt Token expired
            KAP->>OIDC: POST /token (refresh_token grant)<br/>Auth: Client ID/Secret
            OIDC-->>KAP: New Access Token + Refresh Token
            KAP->>Redis: Update session
        end
        KAP->>Upstream: GET /app/resource<br/>X-Forwarded-User: user@email.com<br/>X-Forwarded-Email: user@email.com<br/>X-Forwarded-Groups: group1,group2
        Upstream-->>KAP: 200 OK (response body)
        KAP-->>Browser: 200 OK (proxied response)
    end

    rect rgb(255, 242, 204)
        Note over Browser,K8sAPI: Flow 3: OpenShift OAuth Authentication
        KAP->>K8sAPI: GET /.well-known/oauth-authorization-server<br/>Auth: SA Token, TLS: SA CA
        K8sAPI-->>KAP: OAuth metadata (issuer, endpoints)
        Browser->>KAP: GET /oauth2/start
        KAP->>Browser: 302 Redirect to OpenShift /authorize
        Browser->>OSAuth: GET /authorize?client_id=...<br/>User logs in
        OSAuth->>Browser: 302 Redirect to /oauth2/callback
        Browser->>KAP: GET /oauth2/callback?code=AUTH_CODE
        KAP->>OSAuth: POST /token<br/>Auth: Client ID/Secret, TLS: custom CA
        OSAuth-->>KAP: Access Token
        KAP->>K8sAPI: GET /apis/user.openshift.io/v1/users/~<br/>Auth: Bearer Token, TLS: SA CA
        K8sAPI-->>KAP: User info (name, groups, email)
        KAP->>Browser: Set-Cookie: _oauth2_proxy (session)
    end

    rect rgb(249, 249, 249)
        Note over Envoy,K8sAPI: Flow 4: K8s SA Token + Envoy ext_authz
        Envoy->>KAP: GET /oauth2/auth<br/>Authorization: Bearer <SA token>
        KAP->>K8sAPI: POST /api/v1/tokenreviews<br/>Auth: SA Token, TLS: SA CA
        K8sAPI-->>KAP: TokenReview (authenticated: true, user info)
        KAP-->>Envoy: 202 Accepted<br/>X-Forwarded-User: system:serviceaccount:ns:sa
    end

    rect rgb(252, 232, 232)
        Note over Browser,KAP: Flow 5: Sign-Out with Cleanup
        Browser->>KAP: GET /oauth2/sign_out<br/>Cookie: _oauth2_proxy
        KAP->>Redis: Delete session (if Redis)
        opt OpenShift provider
            KAP->>K8sAPI: DELETE /apis/oauth.openshift.io/v1/oauthaccesstokens/{sha256~hash}<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
        end
        opt OIDC with end_session_endpoint
            KAP->>OIDC: GET /end_session?id_token_hint=...<br/>RP-initiated logout
        end
        KAP->>Browser: Clear cookies + redirect to sign-in
    end
